org.mozilla.javascript.Scriptable
public class AeWSBPELJavaScriptFunctionContainer
extends AeJavaScriptFunctionContainer

This is an extension to the basic JavaScript function container specifically for the WSBPEL namespace. BPEL 2.0 removed getVariableData and getLinkStatus in favor of a shorter $varName and $linkName syntax. However, since BPEL variables cannot be manifested directly as JavaScript variable, the getVariableData and getLinkStatus functions are still used for JavaScript. This class makes these two functions explicitely available, even though they don't exist in the standard BPEL 2.0 function namespace.
